            Access Modifiers:
			- 
            - public
            - private (accessible only from its class)
            - protected (accessible within a package)
            
            
    What is the difference between javac & java?
    javac - compiler generates java bytecode
    
    java - jvm (java virtual machine) executes java bytecodes
            
    Violating access control generates compile error.
 
